{"tid":314142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香燭舖老闆拜神辣著神枱猛噴煙","createTime":"2017-07-09T02:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T02:30:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"193630e7e5c807dfd04f395d8c30724d43286b1d","tid":314142,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083955&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083955%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8c930f15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083955%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=b0b47a84\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083955&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n香燭舖老闆拜神<br />\n辣著神枱猛噴煙<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港仔嘉禾街5-11號一間香燭舖，昨早7時37分，負責人開舖時依習慣拜神，其間火種燃著旁邊雜物起火，大量濃煙冒出，雖然火警觸電自動灑水系統，但仍無法將火救熄，消防接報到場架起升降台開喉撲救，將火救熄，火警中無人受傷。據姓馬街坊表示，火警發生後，香燭舖的負責人逃出店舖求救，並指拜神時燒著神枱，之後波及店內紙紮貨物。"}]}